# CropFresh AI — System Design & Agent Architecture

> Complete system design of the multi-agent RAG platform connecting Karnataka farmers with buyers using AI-powered intelligence.

---

## High-Level Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "User Interfaces"
        WEB["🌐 Web Chat UI"]
        VOICE["🎤 Voice (STT/TTS)"]
        WHATSAPP["📱 WhatsApp Bot"]
        API["⚡ REST API"]
    end

    subgraph "Gateway Layer"
        FASTAPI["FastAPI Server<br/>src/api/main.py"]
        WS["WebSocket Endpoint"]
    end

    subgraph "Orchestration Layer"
        SUPERVISOR["🧠 Supervisor Agent<br/>Query Router"]
        LLM_PROV["LLM Provider<br/>Groq / Bedrock / Together"]
    end

    subgraph "Domain Agents"
        AGRO["🌱 Agronomy Agent"]
        COMMERCE["💰 Commerce Agent"]
        PLATFORM["📱 Platform Agent"]
        GENERAL["👋 General Agent"]
        PRICING["📊 Pricing Agent"]
        VOICE_AG["🗣️ Voice Agent"]
    end

    subgraph "Advanced Agents (Modular)"
        QA["📷 Quality Assessment"]
        BM["🤝 Buyer Matching"]
        PP["📈 Price Prediction"]
        DT["🔬 Digital Twin"]
        CL["📋 Crop Listing"]
        LR["🚚 Logistics Router"]
        ADCL["🌾 ADCL Engine"]
        RESEARCH["🔍 Research Agent"]
    end

    subgraph "RAG Pipeline"
        RAG_GRAPH["LangGraph RAG<br/>(Adaptive+CRAG+Self-RAG)"]
        ORCH["Agentic Orchestrator<br/>Speculative Drafting"]
        KB["Knowledge Base<br/>Qdrant Vector DB"]
        EMBED["Embeddings<br/>all-MiniLM-L6-v2"]
    end

    subgraph "Tools Layer"
        TOOLS["Tool Registry<br/>16+ Tools"]
        AGMARK["Agmarknet Scraper"]
        ENAM["eNAM Client"]
        WEATHER["IMD Weather"]
        NEWS["News Sentiment"]
        ML["ML Forecaster"]
        DEEP["Deep Research"]
        CALC["Calculator"]
        SEARCH["Web Search"]
    end

    subgraph "Data Stores"
        QDRANT["Qdrant Cloud"]
        NEO4J["Neo4j Graph DB"]
        SUPABASE["Supabase PostgreSQL"]
        REDIS["Redis Cache"]
    end

    WEB --> FASTAPI
    VOICE --> WS
    WHATSAPP --> FASTAPI
    API --> FASTAPI
    FASTAPI --> SUPERVISOR
    WS --> VOICE_AG
    SUPERVISOR --> LLM_PROV
    SUPERVISOR --> AGRO & COMMERCE & PLATFORM & GENERAL
    COMMERCE --> PRICING
    AGRO --> KB
    COMMERCE --> KB
    PLATFORM --> KB
    PRICING --> AGMARK & ML & WEATHER & NEWS
    PRICING --> LLM_PROV
    VOICE_AG --> AGRO & PRICING & QA & BM
    QA --> LLM_PROV
    BM --> LLM_PROV
    PP --> ML
    RESEARCH --> DEEP & KB & NEO4J
    RAG_GRAPH --> KB & EMBED
    ORCH --> RAG_GRAPH
    KB --> QDRANT
    TOOLS --> AGMARK & ENAM & WEATHER & NEWS & ML & DEEP & CALC & SEARCH
    AGRO --> LLM_PROV
    GENERAL --> LLM_PROV
```

