### 6. Pricing Agent — *The Dynamic Pricing Engine (DPLE)*

| Property | Detail |
|----------|--------|
| **File** | [pricing_agent.py](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/agents/pricing_agent.py) |
| **Role** | Real-time price recommendations with multi-signal analysis |
| **LLM Connection** | ✅ [_llm_analysis()](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/agents/pricing_agent.py#360-432) — builds rich signal-aware prompt |
| **RAG Connection** | ❌ Uses live data tools instead of RAG |
| **Tools** | Agmarknet scraper, ML Forecaster, Weather tool, News Sentiment |

**Signal pipeline (concurrent):**
```
① Agmarknet live mandi prices      → current price anchor
② ML Forecaster (historical trend)  → 3/7/14-day forecast
③ IMD Weather forecast              → supply disruption signals
④ News Sentiment scraper            → demand shock indicators
```

All 4 signals fetched concurrently via `asyncio.gather()`, then combined into heuristic + LLM analysis.

