### 8. Voice Agent — *The Voice-First Interface*

| Property | Detail |
|----------|--------|
| **File** | [voice_agent.py](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/agents/voice_agent.py) (1040 lines) |
| **Role** | Two-way voice in Hindi/Kannada/English for illiterate farmers |
| **LLM Connection** | ✅ For complex responses after template matching |
| **RAG Connection** | ❌ Routes to other agents which use RAG |
| **Sub-agents** | PricingAgent, AgronomyAgent, QualityAgent, BuyerMatchingAgent, ADCL |

**Voice flow:**
```
Audio → STT (IndicWhisper/MultiProvider) → Text
  → Entity Extraction (VoiceEntityExtractor → VoiceIntent enum)
  → Intent Handler (template-based or agent delegation)
  → Response Text
  → TTS (EdgeTTS/IndicTTS) → Audio Response
```

**Supported intents (14+):**
[create_listing](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/agents/voice_agent.py#447-542), [check_price](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/agents/voice_agent.py#543-582), [track_order](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/agents/voice_agent.py#583-610), [my_listings](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/agents/voice_agent.py#611-633), [find_buyer](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/agents/voice_agent.py#634-697), [check_weather](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/agents/voice_agent.py#698-725), [get_advisory](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/agents/voice_agent.py#726-754), [register](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/tools/registry.py#86-154), [dispute_status](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/agents/voice_agent.py#807-834), [quality_check](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/agents/voice_agent.py#835-875), [greeting](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/agents/general_agent.py#173-194), `help`, `farewell`, `unknown`

