## RAG Pipeline Deep Dive

### Core RAG Graph — [src/rag/graph.py](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/rag/graph.py)

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> AnalyzeQuery
    AnalyzeQuery --> RouteQuery

    state RouteQuery <<choice>>
    RouteQuery --> Retrieve: knowledge/factual
    RouteQuery --> DirectAnswer: greeting/simple

    Retrieve --> GradeDocuments
    
    state GradeDocuments <<choice>>
    GradeDocuments --> Generate: docs relevant
    GradeDocuments --> WebSearch: docs insufficient

    WebSearch --> Generate

    Generate --> CheckHallucination

    state CheckHallucination <<choice>>
    CheckHallucination --> FinalAnswer: grounded
    CheckHallucination --> RetryDecision: hallucination

    state RetryDecision <<choice>>
    RetryDecision --> Retrieve: retries < max
    RetryDecision --> FinalAnswer: max retries reached

    DirectAnswer --> FinalAnswer
    FinalAnswer --> [*]
```

**Pipeline stages:** [RAGState](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/rag/graph.py#17-43) flows through:

| Node | RAG Technique | Purpose |
|------|--------------|---------|
| [analyze_query_node](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/rag/graph.py#77-96) | **Adaptive RAG** | Classify query type, determine routing |
| [retrieve_node](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/rag/graph.py#97-127) | — | Fetch top-K docs from Qdrant via `KnowledgeBase.search()` |
| [grade_documents_node](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/rag/graph.py#128-147) | **Corrective RAG (CRAG)** | Grade doc relevance, decide if web search needed |
| [web_search_node](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/rag/graph.py#148-172) | **CRAG fallback** | Web search when KB docs insufficient |
| [generate_node](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/rag/graph.py#173-223) | — | Build context + system prompt → LLM generation |
| [check_hallucination_node](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/rag/graph.py#224-260) | **Self-RAG** | Verify answer grounded in sources |
| [direct_answer_node](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/rag/graph.py#261-285) | — | Simple queries bypass retrieval |

### Advanced Agentic Orchestrator — [ai/rag/agentic_orchestrator.py](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/ai/rag/agentic_orchestrator.py)

A more sophisticated pipeline (ADR-007) with:

| Component | Role |
|-----------|------|
| **RetrievalPlanner** | LLM-powered tool execution planner (Llama-3.1-8B-Instant) |
| **SpeculativeDraftEngine** | Parallel speculative generation — splits docs into N subsets, generates N drafts, verifier selects best |
| **AgenticSelfEvaluator** | Confidence gating with faithfulness + relevance scores |

---

## LLM Provider Architecture

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class BaseLLMProvider {
        <<abstract>>
        +generate(messages, temperature, max_tokens)
        +stream(messages, temperature, max_tokens)
    }
    
    class GroqProvider {
        -client: AsyncGroq
        -model: "llama-3.3-70b-versatile"
        +generate()
        +stream()
    }
    
    class BedrockProvider {
        -client: boto3.bedrock-runtime
        -models: Claude/Llama/Titan
        +generate() via Converse API
        +stream() via ConverseStream API
    }
    
    class TogetherProvider {
        -client: Together
        -model: configurable
        +generate()
        +stream()
    }
    
    BaseLLMProvider <|-- GroqProvider
    BaseLLMProvider <|-- BedrockProvider
    BaseLLMProvider <|-- TogetherProvider
```

| Provider | Use Case | Default Model |
|----------|----------|---------------|
| **Groq** | Development (fast inference) | `llama-3.3-70b-versatile` |
| **Bedrock** | Production (Claude, Llama, Titan) | `claude-sonnet` (ap-south-1) |
| **Together AI** | Backup | Configurable |

