## Voice Pipeline

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph "Input"
        MIC["🎤 Microphone"]
    end
    
    subgraph "STT Layer"
        WHISPER["IndicWhisper"]
        MULTI_STT["MultiProvider STT"]
    end
    
    subgraph "NLU"
        ENTITY["VoiceEntityExtractor"]
        INTENT["Intent Classification"]
    end
    
    subgraph "Processing"
        TEMPLATE["Template Matching<br/>(14+ intents)"]
        AGENT_DEL["Agent Delegation"]
    end
    
    subgraph "TTS Layer"
        EDGE["EdgeTTS"]
        INDIC["IndicTTS"]
        STREAM["StreamingTTS"]
    end
    
    subgraph "Output"
        SPK["🔊 Speaker"]
    end
    
    MIC --> WHISPER & MULTI_STT
    WHISPER & MULTI_STT --> ENTITY
    ENTITY --> INTENT
    INTENT --> TEMPLATE & AGENT_DEL
    TEMPLATE & AGENT_DEL --> EDGE & INDIC & STREAM
    EDGE & INDIC & STREAM --> SPK
```

**Additional voice components:**
- [vad.py](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/voice/vad.py) — Voice Activity Detection
- [duplex_pipeline.py](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/voice/duplex_pipeline.py) — Full-duplex voice with barge-in support
- [webrtc_transport.py](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/voice/webrtc_transport.py) — WebRTC real-time transport
- [groq_streaming.py](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/voice/groq_streaming.py) / [bedrock_streaming.py](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/voice/bedrock_streaming.py) — Streaming LLM for voice
- `pipecat/` — Pipecat framework integration

