## Data Flow: Complete Query Lifecycle

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor Farmer
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant SUP as Supervisor
    participant LLM as Groq LLM
    participant AGENT as Domain Agent
    participant RAG as RAG Pipeline
    participant KB as Qdrant KB
    participant TOOLS as Tools
    
    Farmer->>API: "What's the tomato price in Bangalore?"
    API->>SUP: process(query, session_id)
    SUP->>LLM: Classify intent
    LLM-->>SUP: { agent: "commerce", confidence: 0.95 }
    SUP->>AGENT: CommerceAgent.process(query)
    
    par Parallel Operations
        AGENT->>RAG: retrieve_context("tomato price Bangalore")
        RAG->>KB: search(query, category="market")
        KB-->>RAG: [matching documents]
        RAG-->>AGENT: formatted context
    and
        AGENT->>TOOLS: PricingAgent.get_recommendation("Tomato", "Bangalore")
        TOOLS->>TOOLS: asyncio.gather(agmarknet, forecast, weather, sentiment)
        TOOLS-->>AGENT: PriceRecommendation
    end
    
    AGENT->>LLM: [system_prompt, context + price_data + query]
    LLM-->>AGENT: Narrative price analysis
    AGENT-->>SUP: AgentResponse
    SUP-->>API: Final response
    API-->>Farmer: "Tomato in Bangalore: ₹25/kg..."
```

---

## BaseAgent Inheritance Pattern

All domain agents follow this pattern from [base_agent.py](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/agents/base_agent.py):

```python
class MyAgent(BaseAgent):
    def __init__(self, llm, tool_registry, state_manager, knowledge_base):
        config = AgentConfig(
            name="my_agent",
            description="...",
            kb_categories=["category1", "category2"],  # RAG filter
            tool_categories=["commerce"],               # Tool access
        )
        super().__init__(config, llm, tool_registry, state_manager, knowledge_base)
    
    def _get_system_prompt(self, context=None) -> str:
        return "Domain-specific system prompt..."
    
    async def process(self, query, context=None, execution=None) -> AgentResponse:
        # 1. RAG retrieval
        docs = await self.retrieve_context(query, categories=self.config.kb_categories)
        
        # 2. Tool usage (optional)
        tool_result = await self.use_tool("tool_name", param1="value")
        
        # 3. LLM generation
        messages = [{"role": "system", "content": self._get_system_prompt()},
                    {"role": "user", "content": f"Context: {docs}\n\nQuery: {query}"}]
        answer = await self.generate_with_llm(messages)
        
        return AgentResponse(content=answer, agent_name=self.name, ...)
```

**Key [BaseAgent](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/agents/base_agent.py#74-414) methods:**

| Method | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| [retrieve_context()](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/agents/base_agent.py#203-246) | Query Qdrant KB with category filters |
| [generate_with_llm()](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/agents/base_agent.py#287-321) | Send messages to LLM provider |
| [use_tool()](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/agents/base_agent.py#247-286) | Execute named tool from registry |
| [format_context()](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/agents/base_agent.py#322-344) | Format retrieved docs for LLM prompt |
| [process_with_stream()](file:///d:/Cropfresh-dev/Cropfresh%20Ai/Cropfresh_Ai/src/agents/base_agent.py#179-202) | Streaming response support |

