## Key Architecture Decisions

| ADR | Decision | Rationale |
|-----|----------|-----------|
| RAG Pipeline | Adaptive + CRAG + Self-RAG hybrid | Query routing + doc grading + hallucination check |
| LLM Strategy | Multi-provider with fallback | Groq (dev) → Bedrock (prod) → Together (backup) |
| Agent Pattern | Supervisor → Domain Agents | Clean separation of concerns, easy to add agents |
| Voice-First | Template matching → LLM fallback | Low latency for common intents, LLM for complex |
| Pricing | 4-signal concurrent pipeline | Comprehensive analysis without serial bottleneck |
| Embeddings | `all-MiniLM-L6-v2` | Fast, lightweight, good multilingual support |
| Vector DB | Qdrant Cloud | Managed service, hybrid search support |
| Graph DB | Neo4j | Entity relationships for research agent |

